title: Looking for a duo partner who can hold his lane and not feed
body: I'm looking for someone who can keep his cool, and also keep his laner not too fed. I'm pretty bummed how most of the time i do perfectly fine in lane, but i look over to my teammates and they're 0/10 (BTW i'm a top main)

replies.body: Sweeeeeet, add me and lets get climbing!
hey there,i wouldnt mind playing with you.
